  <h1>What is Sigfides? — Explained in Plain English</h1>
  <p>
    Sigfides helps businesses fix their core identity signals — name, address, phone, coordinates, schema
    and Google Business Profile — so Google and AI systems can clearly understand who you are,
    where you operate, and how far your relevance extends in the real world.
  </p>

